		<a  href="/health/elderhealth/9267874/Middle-classes-enjoy-13-years-of-healthy-retirement-but-rich-poor-gap-widens.html"><img src="http://i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/01201/PF-Elderlybridge_1201447g.jpg" alt="Middle classes enjoy 13 years of healthy retirement - but rich-poor gap widens" border="0" width="140" height="87" />
							<span class="cornerimagecentre">&nbsp;</span></a>
